1. T(N) = 2T(N-1) + 1
T(N - 1) = 2T(n - 2) + 1
T(N - 2) = 2T(n - 3) + 1

T(n) = 2(2T(n-2) + 1) + 1 = 4T(n - 2) + 3
T(n) = 4(2T(n - 3) + 1) + 3
T(n) = 8T(n-3) + 7

T(n) = (2^k)T(n - k) + (2^k) - 1

If n - k = 0
n = k
T(n) = 2T(0) + 1
T(n) = 2 + 1 = 3

Time complexity: Î˜(1)  

